# Environment Variables Template for Vercel Deployment
# Copy these to your Vercel Dashboard Environment Variables

# Database Configuration
DATABASE_URL=your_neon_postgresql_connection_string_here

# Node Environment
NODE_ENV=production

# Optional: Add other environment variables your app needs
# JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_here
# API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to Vercel Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# 2. Add each variable above with your actual values
# 3. Make sure to set the Environment to "Production", "Preview", and "Development" as needed 